Package: python-blimpy
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python:Depends}
Provides: ${python:Provides}
Description: Breakthrough Listen I/O Methods (python 2 library)
 python readers for interacting with Sigproc filterbank (.fil), HDF5 (.h5) and
 guppi raw (.raw) files generated by the Breakthrough Listen instruments.

